1
00:00:00,567 --> 00:00:01,468
Hey!

2
00:00:01,468 --> 00:00:04,838
Keep the room well‐lit and
watch from a distance, ha‐hey?

3
00:01:51,044 --> 00:01:52,379
Who art thou?

4
00:01:59,786 --> 00:02:01,421
My name is Gankeimaru.

5
00:02:01,822 --> 00:02:03,390
If you cherish your life,
drop the sword

6
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:04,958
you are wearing
and leave at once.

7
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:06,293
Alas, I see.

8
00:02:06,393 --> 00:02:08,929
So thou art the ogre whom
hath been hunting swords

9
00:02:08,929 --> 00:02:11,131
and causing a public
disturbance here.

10
00:02:11,565 --> 00:02:12,566
Most well met.

11
00:02:12,766 --> 00:02:13,867
If thou desirest my sword,

12
00:02:13,867 --> 00:02:16,636
then summon thine own
and take it by force!

13
00:02:26,947 --> 00:02:29,082
Die!

14
00:02:52,339 --> 00:02:53,640
That was too easy.

15
00:02:53,807 --> 00:02:57,010
The only impressive thing about you
is the sword you carry, eh?

16
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:59,846
This is far from the
strongest sword I've seen.

17
00:03:00,113 --> 00:03:03,417
I heard that a samurai's blade
can cut apart even a star,

18
00:03:03,583 --> 00:03:06,086
but it seems coming to Earth
was a big waste of time.

19
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:08,755
Oh, where is it, I wonder.

20
00:03:09,056 --> 00:03:11,491
The legendary sword, "Star Destroyer"?

21
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:18,832
Ouch!

22
00:03:19,032 --> 00:03:20,400
Oh, my god, just look!

23
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,836
Long hours as a manga artist
have turned my stomach

24
00:03:22,836 --> 00:03:24,571
into a double cheeseburger!

25
00:03:24,571 --> 00:03:27,074
