if I look like this!

26
00:03:27,941 --> 00:03:29,543
What's the matter, Michael?

27
00:03:29,843 --> 00:03:32,813
Did a dip pen pierce your biceps
and make them explode, huh?

28
00:03:32,813 --> 00:03:34,081
No, woman!

29
