Look at this, Marilyn.

30
00:03:35,649 --> 00:03:37,050
Look at my fat stomach!

31
00:03:37,350 --> 00:03:38,618
You need to be careful.

32
00:03:38,718 --> 00:03:41,421
Dip pens are sharp enough to
kill people, you know that?

33
00:03:41,521 --> 00:03:44,224
