stupid woman!

34
00:03:44,224 --> 00:03:45,358
‐It's my stomach!
‐Oh, okay!

35
00:03:45,358 --> 00:03:46,426
Don't worry!

36
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:49,096
Just use the "Round‐and‐Round
Fat Burning Down" Machine!

37
00:03:49,096 --> 00:03:51,698
Just do this for just twelve hours
every day, and your stomach fat

38
00:03:51,698 --> 00:03:54,568
will melt away right
before your very eyes!

39
00:03:54,701 --> 00:03:55,502
Come on!

40
00:03:55,502 --> 00:03:57,137
<i>Are you serious, Marilyn?</i>

41
00:03:57,137 --> 00:03:57,838
<i>Yes!</i>

42
00:03:57,838 --> 00:04:00,240
<i>Order right now and you'll also</i>
<i>get the blue and red versions</i>

43
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,976
<i>on top of the yellow for</i>
<i>this incredibly low price!</i>

44
00:04:03,143 --> 00:04:04,511
<i>Just pay in 12 monthly installments,</i>

45
00:04:04,511 --> 00:04:06,213
<i>and</i> <i>you'll</i> <i>get</i> <i>the</i> <i>body</i>
<i>of</i> <i>your</i> <i>dreams!</i>

46
00:04:06,213 --> 00:04:08,515
<i>And</i> <i>then</i> <i>it's</i> <i>goodbye</i> <i>to</i>
<i>my</i> <i>double</i> <i>cheeseburger!</i>

47
00:04:08,515 --> 00:04:10,150
<i>‐Yahoo!</i>
‐Yahoo!

48
00:04:10,450 --> 00:04:12,152
"Yahoo" my ass, dummy.

49
00:04:12,285 --> 00:04:13,987
Where did you get that stupid thing?

50
00:04:14,454 --> 00:04:16,123
I called that number and
they gave it to me.

51
00:04:16,123 --> 00:04:18,525
They gave me this, and this,
and this, and this, too.

52
00:04:18,525 --> 00:04:20,093
‐Yahoo!
‐Good god!

53
00:04:20,227 --> 00:04:21,995
Hey, Kagura,
you know this is called...

54
00:04:21,995 --> 00:04:23,663
