55
00:04:23,663 --> 00:04:25,665
It's a show where
people sell things.

56
00:04:25,799 --> 00:04:28,068
Those things weren't free;
you bought them all.

57
00:04:28,068 --> 00:04:29,002
Seriously?

58
00:04:29,002 --> 00:04:31,037
You should return those
items immediately.

59
00:04:31,171 --> 00:04:33,140
They'll probably take
them back if you call.

60
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:35,475
Hey, that's not very funny
for a joke, Johnny!

61
00:04:35,475 --> 00:04:37,010
Who're you calling Johnny?

62
00:04:37,210 --> 00:04:38,812
Oh,Shinpachi, give me a hand.

63
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:40,347
We're returning all of this.

64
00:04:40,547 --> 00:04:41,715
Right.

65
00:04:44,184 --> 00:04:46,052
No, don't, give them back!

66
00:04:46,353 --> 00:04:47,554
Johnny!

67
00:04:47,554 --> 00:04:49,022
Depperson!

68
00:04:50,157 --> 00:04:52,225
This is so unfair, damn it!

69
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:55,262
What if I end up with a
double cheeseburger?

70
00:04:55,295 --> 00:04:56,496
Stupid Gin!

71
00:04:56,763 --> 00:05:00,100
Grown ups just don't
understand anything!

72
00:05:01,802 --> 00:05:02,869
Oh...

73
00:05:03,069 --> 00:05:04,704
Oh.

74
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:08,975
Hmm... Well this isn't it, either...

75
00:05:09,376 --> 00:05:10,877
Hey!
What're you doing?

76
00:05:12,612 --> 00:05:14,514
What're you doing walking
around with a bunch of swords

77
00:05:14,514 --> 00:05:16,650
