483
00:21:36,595 --> 00:21:38,364
There is a strange rumor
going around the city.

484
00:21:38,931 --> 00:21:40,866
Something about these being
man eating cockroaches

485
00:21:40,866 --> 00:21:43,202
that came from outer space to
take over the whole Earth.

486
00:21:43,335 --> 00:21:45,471
And the world is doomed unless
we kill the queen cockroach,

487
00:21:45,471 --> 00:21:47,439
with "GORO" written on
its back or something.

488
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:49,608
Man, people will believe anything!

489
00:21:50,309 --> 00:21:51,510
Shinpachi...

490
00:21:51,744 --> 00:21:52,878
say that again.

491
00:21:53,345 --> 00:21:55,447
Like I said, these are
man‐eating cockroaches...

492
00:21:55,681 --> 00:21:56,816
and unless we kill
the queen roach

493
00:21:56,816 --> 00:21:58,250
that has "GORO"
written on its back,

494
00:21:58,250 --> 00:21:59,952
the entire Earth is doomed.

495
00:22:00,085 --> 00:22:01,687
Isn't that stupid or what?

496
00:22:06,158 --> 00:22:07,793
That is pretty laughable.

497
00:22:08,060 --> 00:22:08,894
I guess I'm...

498
00:22:08,894 --> 00:22:11,163
the devil who destroyed
the entire world.

499
00:22:11,764 --> 00:22:13,666
I can't do anything other than laugh.

500
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:15,668
You've seen it?

501
00:22:15,801 --> 00:22:17,770
You saw the GORO roach!

502
00:22:18,370 --> 00:22:21,674
I had it in my hand and then
I let it go and doomed Earth.

503
00:22:22,274 --> 00:22:23,542
Wh‐Wh‐Where is it?

504
00:22:23,542 --> 00:22:25,244
We have to find it right away.

505
00:22:25,244 --> 00:22:26,145
It's no use.

506
00:22:26,145 --> 00:22:27,479
It ran off somewhere.

507
00:22:27,479 --> 00:22:28,747
Forget it.
Let's go eat steak.

508
00:22:29,782 --> 00:22:31,850
Come on, Kagura, you can
eat all you want today.

509
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:33,819
We're gonna die, after all.

510
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:35,888
I basically just condemned
us all to death.

511
00:22:36,188 --> 00:22:37,122
‐Kill me now.
‐Wait, hey Gin!

512
00:22:37,122 --> 00:22:38,624
Pull yourself together!

513
00:22:38,857 --> 00:22:39,858
‐Hey, Gin!
‐Kill me!

514
00:24:37,242 --> 00:24:38,911
Excuse me everyone...

515
00:24:39,345 --> 00:24:40,713
but please hear me out...

516
00:24:42,214 --> 00:24:44,350
I assume the killer is flat broke.

517
00:24:44,483 --> 00:24:46,051
So I think we should slap all
suspects with a fat stack of bills

518
00:24:46,051 --> 00:24:47,686
‐until they spill the beans.
‐What's going on?

519
00:24:47,686 --> 00:24:48,721
What's next week's story about?

